README.html.title: Cursor Pagination | cursor-site
README.html.summary: Cursor Pagination The application, developed in NET9, implements pagination using a cursor. The cursor contains information regarding the last ID of the table from which pagination starts, a generic object that holds the search parameters, and the index from which pagination begins.
